content.value: This well designed, full-size, beautiful Italian leather tote bag is perfect for your everyday needs. Includes all the inner organization to keep you on track throughout the day including a 13" laptop slip, iPhone pocket, zipper pocket, plus several other pockets and a hook for your keys. Your go-to everyday tote, no doubt.
Size: 11" H x 18" W x 5" D - 10" shoulder strap drop
Materials: the finest top-grain Italian leather; gold hardware
Features: poly-satin interior with 13" laptop slip, zipper pocket, key hook and iPhone pocket
Weight: Bag weighs 1.8 lbs when empty
When dirty, give it a quick wipe with a soft dry cloth; with it you can use some leather cleansing cream or a small amount of water; let water spills dry naturally.
